OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder James Holder found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FThe co-founder of clothing firm
OL,7,FSuperdry is facing jail after being
OL,8,Ffound guilty of raping a woman after a
OL,9,Fnight out drinking.
OL,11,FJames Holder, 54, had denied charges
OL,12,Fof assault by penetration and rape and
OL,13,Fsaid what sexual activity took place
OL,14,Fbetween them was consensual.
OL,16,FA jury at Gloucester Crown Court,
OL,17,Fsitting in Cirencester, acquitted
OL,18,FHolder of assault by penetration but
OL,19,Ffound him guilty of rape.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
