OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777709146
OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder James Holder found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FThe court heard the woman was attacked
OL,7,Fin the early hours of May 7 2022 after
OL,8,Fa night out at a bar in Cheltenham.
OL,10,FHolder and a friend had gone back to
OL,11,Fher home uninvited, and he attacked
OL,12,Fher after waking from a short nap on
OL,13,Fher bed.
OL,15,FGiving evidence, the woman said she
OL,16,Fwas crying and asking the married
OL,17,Ffather of two to stop, but he carried
OL,18,Fon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
