PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777709146
OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder James Holder found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FThe ordeal ended when she managed to
OL,7,Fescape the bedroom, and Holder left
OL,8,Fher home a short time later.
OL,10,FUnder cross-examination, Holder denied
OL,11,Fthe reason he had gone to the woman's
OL,12,Fhome was that he "saw an opportunity
OL,13,Fto have sex with her".
OL,26,@tD@ROUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
