CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777709146
OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder James Holder found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FJames Haskell, prosecuting, asked:
OL,7,F"You saw something you wanted and you
OL,8,Ftook it, because the truth is that
OL,9,Fwhen you got to the doorway of the
OL,10,Fliving room you said something like:
OL,11,F'What's happening, is everything all
OL,12,Fright?' as you wanted to entice her to
OL,13,Fthe bedroom and that's why you said:
OL,14,F'Can you show me?'
OL,16,F"It ended because she managed to
OL,17,Fescape off the bed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
